        <mxCell id="wb" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#7A6000;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="Treating blast radius analysis as excessive caution rather than a proportionate response to a genuinely asymmetric risk profile. The staged autonomy model exists specifically because of this asymmetry. Teams that skip the analysis are not being bolder; they are transferring the downside risk to the incidents that follow." vertex="1">
